title: G1 support/fill main LF duo/team
body:
I am a support main who can do every other role well. I need of a partner to learn more and climb S9 and S10.  Unfortunately I started the climb late by myself and have experienced terrible sportsmanship from others/dc etc “ you know “

I am a previous season Diamond/plat ranks support/fill.

Karma-Lulu-Nami #1 picks
Blitz-Soraka-Nautilus #2 picks

I am also interested in a 5v5 Ranked team to join.

Brisbane - AEST - 3pm + weekdays. And weekends at anytime.

replies.body: I'm an ad carry main who is looking for a sup main to climb with as well, I'm D4 in flex and Plat 2 in solo q looking to climb to high diamond before the season ends. I added your league name, my discord name is JayydotAU#3648, send me a request and we can talk there.
